data.description: Welcome to this recently built (2018) custom Palace Home located in the exclusive gated community of Cedar Heights! As you enter the courtyard you are welcomed by imported Indian doors and a "European" fountain! From the courtyard you enter the custom steel door and are greeted by hand laid Brick flooring, reclaimed Kentucky bourbon barrel wood beams and the grand floating stairs! As you enter the open concept main level featuring the grand floating staircase, a formal dining room with double sided gas fireplace, a formal living room on the other side of the fireplace, art display loft and atrium all framed by tall ceilings and multiple skylights for all the natural light. From the Atrium or dining room you enter the open concept kitchen. The kitchen has a specially designed "concertina" window, hand painted/decoupage wall tiles, wood burning stove, induction stove top, double oven, travertine floor tiles, large walk-in pantry and your own garden room with access to the balcony. Also, the main level has an art studio/bedroom with double pocket doors completed with imported Ukrainian pulls, a sitting area, a laundry room, a 1/2 bath, and access to a private courtyard. Off of the living room is a sunroom which has 3 skylights, a built in South African style "Braai"/BBQ and a walk out to the balcony. Following the floating stairway up to the next level you are greeted by the landing/library with "Juliet" balcony. This leads to the Primary Suite and office/5th bedroom. The Primary suite features a gas fireplace, sitting area, access to the private wrap around balcony and large 5-piece custom bathroom that includes a spa tub, walk-in shower, atrium, changing room and walk-in closet. The lower level of this beautiful home features 2 additional bedrooms, each with its own ensuite bathroom and walk out to a patio. This level also has a family room, kitchenette, home theatre, sauna, recreation room, recreation area with a walk out to a patio, utility room and a safe room!
